{"tid":1009632,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【Apex Legends】今日出嘅免費大逃殺game有無人玩？","createTime":"2019-02-05T10:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T05:28:29.000Z","uid":229553,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4d53e38a8bd66966bb307b40a86c6427e8f564dd","tid":1009632,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"畫面幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人留Origin ID一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAPEX LEGENDS 並沒有常見的故事模式或單人模式，玩家可以和朋友或任何其他網上玩家組成3人 小隊進行遊戲，和遊戲中另外   20組   3人小隊( 合共 60 位玩家)進行大逃殺對戰。一如其他同類遊戲，手無寸鐵的玩家一開始需要由飛機跳下，選擇合適的地方盡快尋找武器及裝備。而在 APEX LEGENDS 中，遊戲會以 4 個回合的方式進行(每個回合 4 分鐘)，而地圖亦會不斷收窄令玩家更快遇見敵人，確保不會純粹在地圖上亂走大海撈針。<br />\nunwire遊戲介紹：<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/02/05/apex-legends-test/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F02%2F05%2Fapex-legends-test%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=fe003c9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/02/05/apex-legends-test/game-channel/</a><br />\nOrigin平台裝遊戲：<a href=\"https://www.origin.com/hkg/zh-tw/store\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.origin.com%2Fhkg%2Fzh-tw%2Fstore&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=718e6bc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.origin.com/hkg/zh-tw/store</a><br />\n廣東話遊戲介紹：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FLNh2f3cPJU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFLNh2f3cPJU&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFqd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=8892e4d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FLNh2f3cPJU</a>"},{"pid":"f954eccb637449640cb55a3d8881f0c98e7609f3","tid":1009632,"uid":156747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"discord<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/MjgYzDn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/li